## English

This repository contains the CubePay API documentation, SDK, integration examples,
and implementation guides. It does **not** contain the source code of the CubePay
core platform (including bank SMS detection, wallet management, merchant panel,
or backend infrastructure), which is proprietary, private, and runs exclusively
on CubePay servers.

### You may:

- Use, copy, modify, and integrate the files in this repository (including
  CubePayClient.php, examples, and documentation) to connect your own website,
  bot, or application to the CubePay service.
- Use these files in both personal and commercial projects.

### You may NOT:

- Use this documentation to build, promote, or provide a competing or similar
  payment service, with or without the CubePay name.
- Use the CubePay name or logo to promote any product or service other than a
  genuine integration with the CubePay platform.
- Claim ownership or authorship of the CubePay service.

These files are provided **"AS IS"**, without any express or implied warranty.
CubePay shall not be liable for any damages resulting from the use or misuse of
these files.

For licensing or partnership inquiries, contact: @cube_sup

